description:
This is a 31 minute workout called '30 MINUTE HIIT | Treadmill Workout Follow Along #IBXRunning' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Let's HIIT is Hard with this 30 minute treadmill workout! Follow along with coach Rachael as we are going to sweat our way through these HIIT intervals and come out the other side feeling accomplished!

30:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Veronica's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bodibyroni/
Rachael's Instragram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/

00:00 - Intro
00:33 - Warm Up
5:33 - Workout!
28:33 - Cool Down

Workout Structure:
Warmup: 5 minutes 
HIIT Workout - Repeat 8 times
      HIIT Interval: 1 minute - Speed increases by 0.2 each segment
      RECOVER: 1 minute
End with two 3-minute long runs!
Cooldown at the end!

Songs Used:
1. Another Kind - Mindme
2. Astral Projection - Hallmore
3. Better on the Weekend - Russell Vista...
